610
00:32:41,100 --> 00:32:42,700
No, it wouldn't.

611
00:32:45,830 --> 00:32:47,100
Mm.

612
00:32:49,530 --> 00:32:51,460
Quiet, everyone.

613
00:32:51,500 --> 00:32:53,060
She's coming. Move it.

614
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:02,760
Surprise!

615
00:33:02,800 --> 00:33:06,130
