642
00:34:31,260 --> 00:34:32,760
We'll alert the hospital.

643
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:36,030
- We're gonna need a psych evaluation.  - Thank you. Thank you.

644
00:34:38,330 --> 00:34:42,260
