A glass of champagne.

666
00:36:18,730 --> 00:36:20,700
She's tough.

667
00:36:20,730 --> 00:36:22,660
I'm sure she'll be okay.

668
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:25,200
How about the crazy married couple throwing drinks?

669
00:36:25,230 --> 00:36:27,960
How are they gonna be?

670
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:30,000
You know,I just thought that you got it,

